 uncert.
 } (
\backslash
sqrt{
\backslash
sum w_i^2}) 
\backslash
text{ when nominal yield} 
\backslash
neq 0
\backslash

\backslash
 
\backslash
text{upper limit (1.14 lumi rescaled) when yield}=0  
\backslash
